### 1. 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8091/api/health

### 2. 上传文档
POST http://localhost:8091/api/knowledge-bases/kb-test-001/documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary123

--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.txt"

这是一个测试文档的内容。
电力设备运行规程中规定，变压器油温异常时应立即检查冷却系统。

--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="tags"

{"专业":"电力"}
--boundary123--

### 3. 文档列表
GET http://localhost:8091/api/knowledge-bases/kb-test-001/documents?page=1&pageSize=20

### 4. 文档详情（替换为你的文档ID）
GET http://localhost:8091/api/documents/14c1c18d972b4523971a402f1432fa87

### 5. 查看切片
GET http://localhost:8091/api/documents/892f1bf5cdb145feb56035f079cd0ebe/chunks?page=1&pageSize=50

### 6. 下载文档
GET http://localhost:8091/api/documents/892f1bf5cdb145feb56035f079cd0ebe/download

### 7. 更新标签
PUT http://localhost:8091/api/documents/892f1bf5cdb145feb56035f079cd0ebe/tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tags": {
    "专业": "电力",
    "设备": "变压器"
  }
}

### 8. 删除文档
DELETE http://localhost:8091/api/knowledge-bases/kb-test-001/documents/892f1bf5cdb145feb56035f079cd0ebe

### 9. 批量删除
POST http://localhost:8091/api/knowledge-bases/kb-test-001/documents/batch-delete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": ["文档ID1", "文档ID2"]
}

### 10. 重试处理
POST http://localhost:8091/api/documents/14c1c18d972b4523971a402f1432fa87/retry
### 11. 检索测试（vector_rerank 模式）
POST http://localhost:8091/api/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "变压器油温异常如何处理",
  "knowledgeBaseIds": ["kb-test-001"],
  "topK": 10,
  "searchMode": "vector_rerank",
  "similarityThreshold": 0.6,
  "rerankThreshold": 0.5,
  "tagFilters": {
    "专业": "汽机"
  }
}

### 12. 检索测试（纯向量模式）
POST http://localhost:8091/api/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "设备巡检周期",
  "knowledgeBaseIds": [],
  "topK": 5,
  "searchMode": "vector",
  "similarityThreshold": 0.7
}

### 13. 知识库列表（对外 API - 供问答/报告组消费）
GET http://localhost:8091/api/knowledge-bases?page=1&pageSize=20

### 14. 知识库列表 - 按类型筛选
GET http://localhost:8091/api/knowledge-bases?docType=规程规范&page=1&pageSize=20

### 15. 知识库列表 - 按关键词搜索
GET http://localhost:8091/api/knowledge-bases?keyword=规程&page=1&pageSize=20

### 16. 知识库详情（对外 API）
GET http://localhost:8091/api/knowledge-bases/kb-test-001


### 17. 测试 400 错误（上传不支持的格式）
POST http://localhost:8091/api/knowledge-bases/kb-test-001/documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary123

--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.exe"

fake exe content
--boundary123--

### 18. 测试 404 错误（查询不存在的文档）
GET http://localhost:8091/api/documents/nonexistent-id-12345

### 19. 测试标签独立持久化
PUT http://localhost:8091/api/documents/你的文档ID/tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tags": {
    "颜色": "红色"
  }
}

### 20. 测试 3-3：越权删除拦截（用错误的知识库删文档）
DELETE http://localhost:8091/api/knowledge-bases/kb-test-002/documents/9b0f0526046b4d8a8dd8dca5c685cd34

### 21. 正常删除（用于对比）
DELETE http://localhost:8091/api/knowledge-bases/kb-test-001/documents/9b0f0526046b4d8a8dd8dca5c685cd34

